title: Commander Keen in Holiday Hijinx!
content:
Firstly: This isn't Keen Dreams 3D, I'm afraid, which I'm still trying to finish...[img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-crazy.gif[/img]

Also, I know Christmas is over, but usher in the new year of 2005 with this fangame that I made in the time frame of a month...Commander Keen in: Holiday Hijinx! (The Lost Christmas Episode) [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-christmas.gif[/img]

The story is this: Billy Blaze is lying in bed, awaiting Santa Claus, when all of a sudden, he hears strange blasting noises downstairs. Donning his stun gun and his brother's football helmet, he rushes down to the living room to see blast burns and purple slime all over his living room, and NO PRESENTS! Standing out is a note near the hole in the wall, which he soon discovers is from the wicked and disgusting Snoutians (basically these yellow things with four eyes, one foot, and big nostrils) of Wintra VII, who've kidnapped Santa Claus! Keen is curious that no ransom was asked for (the possibility of the whole thing being a trap never occurs to him[img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-mortlol.gif[/img] ), but Christmas is at stake and Santa must be rescued! Keen hops in the BWB-MR and heads for Wintra VII to rescue his eight presents and Santa Claus.

This new fangame is the first to showcase the Keen sprite and isometric engine I've developed in Games Factory that I'll probably re-use for my future Keen fangames, tweaking stuff and making it better with each game.[img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-yorp.gif[/img]

I've sent the ZIP to Xtraverse via www.yousendit.com , hopefully he can get it up soon and you guys can download it (please don't have this topic deleted in the meantime)...[img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-grin.gif[/img]
